com.nm.ignite.gagrid.samples.movie

Class MovieFitnessFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nm.ignite.gagrid.samples.movie.MovieFitnessFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFitnessFunction

    public class MovieFitnessFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFitnessFunction
    This example demonstrates how to create a IFitnessFunction Your IFitness function will vary depending on your particular use case. For this fitness function, we simply want to calculate the value of an individual solution relative to other solutions. To do this, we simply increase fitness score by number of times genre is found in list of movies. In addition, we increase score by fictional IMDB rating. If there are duplicate movies in selection, we automatically apply a '0' fitness score.
